                      "ep_id": 7472,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Хаборим",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Although Tenoch agreed to the current Pyro Archon",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7299,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/12/30/2f098b1f15854fd9dafc54998795a59e_864981592196815761.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Mavuika",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "'s plan to fight the Abyss, he promised to find a way to collect the debt. During the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_1090730713764694732.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Катаклизм в Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", he became the leader of the tribal coalition forces.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7493,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Ванджиру",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The great runner from the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7000,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/29/237301566/34cbc5aa060896e731bea85173816bed_7751929454071826209.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Удел Благодатных Земель",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "and a hero of Natlan, who was first to join Tenoch along with her companion, Kayeke.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7494,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Менелик",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "One of the six heroes of Natlan and a warrior from the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6999,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/29/237301566/b3db302029d76613e2bfa33f036c565c_4703083528994467732.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Клан Цветочного Пера",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Along with his companion, Ngoubou, he was the second to join Tenoch.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7495,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Санхадж",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Sanhaj Kompore from the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6998,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/11/24/237301566/0ed9af441ff862c8caccc8ba87d3f4e8_3382131558213222413.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Повелители Ночного Ветра",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "had foreseen his and Tenoch's heroic end, and how the place that would become known as the \"Mare Jivari\" in later days would be born but still joined Tenoch with his companion, Mahamba. Since Tenoch lost his Ancient Name, the Ode of Resurrection couldn't bring him back.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7496,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Буркина",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "One of the six heroes of Natlan and a courier from the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6996,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/05/237301566/79ebff2a0e10528e9129a10ee3043668_5764817952363516280.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Потомки Крон",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". He was the forth to join Tenoch along with his companion, Kongamato.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7492,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Сундиата",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "A chief of the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6995,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/05/237301566/eb438f45c1b23162d4b17505fc6b0205_4048251979466285119.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Дети Эха",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "and one of the six heroes of natlan. Before the Cataclysm, he petitioned the Pyro Archon to vote for Tenoch's expulsion because of his love for fighting. Sundjatta and his companion Muhuru were the fifth to join Tenoch in the battle with the Abyss.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7491,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Тупак",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Tenoch's greatest foe of youth, a giant from the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6997,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/05/237301566/bf4346b2af8799209a3a494f359067a7_8906688900072372819.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Народ Родников",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Tenoch left him over 300 scars, 20 broken bones, and over 100 shards of obsidian buried deep within his flesh. Tupac was the last to join Tenoch.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
